engths → 400\n- Missing auth → 401 or 403 as applicable\n- Wrong role → 403 where applicable\n- Non-existent resources → 404 where applicable\n- Conflict/duplicate → 409 where applicable\n\n---\n\n## RED Phase Status\n\nAll tests are designed to FAIL in the RED phase because:\n- Feature modules (AuthModule, PropertiesModule, FavoritesModule, etc.) are NOT registered in `createTestApp()`\n- No controllers/routes exist yet — all requests will 404\n- Mock tokens are placeholders (not real JWT-signed tokens)\n- Implementation is expected in the GREEN phase\n\nTo run tests:\n```bash\ncd backend\nnpx jest --config test/jest-e2e.json\n```\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/BACKEND_TESTS_GENERATED.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/status/BACKEND_TESTS_GENERATED.md","time":{"start":1779246618187,"end":1779246618499}},"id":"prt_e435c1fd9001WfP7fhHOJwR5d9","sessionID":"ses_1bcacaf85ffekWeHxJzinOBzsU","messageID":"msg_e435ae833001tjPQT2kU0uA4Cb"}}
